              </respStmt>
              <colophon>Colophon: iti śrībrahmāṃdapurāṇe pārvatā iṃdrāṇīsaṃvāde pīṭhorākhyavratakathā samāptaḥ // śake 1723 duramatīnāmasaṃvatsare bhādrapadakṣukla caturthyāṃ bhṛguvāsare tadine dāḍekaropajāmakabhāskarena likhitaṃ // cha // śubhaṃbhavata // cha // (f. 7v-8r).</colophon>
